{"word":"ἦχος","slug":"ἦχος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἦχος, ου, ὁ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἠχέω\">ἠχέω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> of a sound that spreads out and makes an impact, <b>gust <a href='B:510 2:2'>Ac 2:2</a>; blast, blare <a href='B:650 12:19'>Hb 12:19</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> of information going out from place to place <b>news <a href='B:490 4:37'>Lk 4:37</a>.</b><p class=\"br\"/><b><el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἦχος\">ἦχος</a>, ους, τό</el></b> [late <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ nt.\">nt.</a> form of the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prec.\">prec.</a>] of noise made by a tempestuous sea <b>roar <a href='B:490 21:25'>Lk 21:25</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἤχθην\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἡψάμην\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}